{"tha-ap35:0.1":"Therapadana ","tha-ap35:0.2":"Kundadhanavagga ","tha-ap35:0.3":"3 Mahakaccanattheraapadana ","tha-ap35:1.1":"“Padumuttaranathassa, ","tha-ap35:1.2":"padumam nama cetiyam; ","tha-ap35:1.3":"Silasanam karayitva, ","tha-ap35:1.4":"suvannenabhilepayim. ","tha-ap35:2.1":"Ratanamayachattanca, ","tha-ap35:2.2":"paggayha valabijanim; ","tha-ap35:2.3":"Buddhassa abhiropesim, ","tha-ap35:2.4":"lokabandhussa tadino. ","tha-ap35:3.1":"Yavata devata bhumma, ","tha-ap35:3.2":"sabbe sannipatum tada; ","tha-ap35:3.3":"Ratanamayachattanam, ","tha-ap35:3.4":"vipakam kathayissati. ","tha-ap35:4.1":"Tanca sabbam sunissama, ","tha-ap35:4.2":"kathayantassa satthuno; ","tha-ap35:4.3":"Bhiyyo hasam janeyyama, ","tha-ap35:4.4":"sammasambuddhasasane. ","tha-ap35:5.1":"Hemasane nisiditva, ","tha-ap35:5.2":"sayambhu aggapuggalo; ","tha-ap35:5.3":"Bhikkhusanghaparibyulho, ","tha-ap35:5.4":"ima gatha abhasatha. ","tha-ap35:6.1":"‘Yenidam asanam dinnam, ","tha-ap35:6.2":"sovannam ratanamayam; ","tha-ap35:6.3":"Tamaham kittayissami, ","tha-ap35:6.4":"sunatha mama bhasato. ","tha-ap35:7.1":"Timsa kappani devindo, ","tha-ap35:7.2":"devarajjam karissati; ","tha-ap35:7.3":"Samanta yojanasatam, ","tha-ap35:7.4":"abhayabhibhavissati. ","tha-ap35:8.1":"Manussalokamagantva, ","tha-ap35:8.2":"cakkavatti bhavissati; ","tha-ap35:8.3":"Pabhassaroti namena, ","tha-ap35:8.4":"uggatejo bhavissati. ","tha-ap35:9.1":"Diva va yadi va rattim, ","tha-ap35:9.2":"sataramsiva uggato; ","tha-ap35:9.3":"Samanta attharatanam, ","tha-ap35:9.4":"ujjotissati khattiyo. ","tha-ap35:10.1":"Kappasatasahassamhi, ","tha-ap35:10.2":"okkakakulasambhavo; ","tha-ap35:10.3":"Gotamo nama gottena, ","tha-ap35:10.4":"sattha loke bhavissati. ","tha-ap35:11.1":"Tusita hi cavitvana, ","tha-ap35:11.2":"sukkamulena codito; ","tha-ap35:11.3":"Kaccano nama namena, ","tha-ap35:11.4":"brahmabandhu bhavissati. ","tha-ap35:12.1":"So paccha pabbajitvana, ","tha-ap35:12.2":"araha hessatinasavo; ","tha-ap35:12.3":"Gotamo lokapajjoto, ","tha-ap35:12.4":"aggatthane thapessati. ","tha-ap35:13.1":"Sankhittapucchitam panham, ","tha-ap35:13.2":"Vittharena kathessati; ","tha-ap35:13.3":"Kathayanto ca tam panham, ","tha-ap35:13.4":"Ajjhasayam purayissati’. ","tha-ap35:14.1":"Addhe kule abhijato, ","tha-ap35:14.2":"brahmano mantaparagu; ","tha-ap35:14.3":"Ohaya dhanadhannani, ","tha-ap35:14.4":"pabbajim anagariyam. ","tha-ap35:15.1":"Sankhittenapi pucchante, ","tha-ap35:15.2":"vittharena kathemaham; ","tha-ap35:15.3":"Ajjhasayam tesam puremi, ","tha-ap35:15.4":"tosemi dvipaduttamam. ","tha-ap35:16.1":"Tosito me mahaviro, ","tha-ap35:16.2":"sayambhu aggapuggalo; ","tha-ap35:16.3":"Bhikkhusanghe nisiditva, ","tha-ap35:16.4":"etadagge thapesi mam. ","tha-ap35:17.1":"Patisambhida catasso, ","tha-ap35:17.2":"…pe… ","tha-ap35:17.3":"katam buddhassa sasanam”. ","tha-ap35:18.1":"Ittham sudam ayasma mahakaccano thero ima gathayo abhasitthati. ","tha-ap35:19.1":"Mahakaccanattherassapadanam tatiyam. "}